CatDescriptText: Image published in advertisement in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 4, 1946, pg. 20, with portions of text reading: "The Three Musketeers present The May Queen Frolic, Walt Harper His Piano and His Orchestra...  Cottage Inn, 525 Homewood Avenue, Friday Night, May 3rd..."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of seven women, contestants for May Queen, posed on and around bench in Harris Studio
